Package: vision
Type: Package
Title: Schema Validation and Recipe Construction for Consumer Psychology Research
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(
    person("Niche", "Contributors", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "niche@example.com")
    )
Description: Provides spec-first workflow infrastructure for consumer psychology
    research. Parses and validates YAML/JSON specification files, constructs
    auditable analysis recipes, and enforces schema compliance without performing
    data ingestion, modeling, or reporting. Part of the 'niche' R universe for
    reproducible consumer research.
